text: Freddie James Prinze (born Frederick Karl Pruetzel; June 22-1954 - January 29, 1977) was an American stand-up comedian and actor. == Early life == Prinze was born in New York City to Edward Karl Pruetzel and Aurea Elana Ruiz. His father was German and his mother was Puerto Rican. == Personal life == Prinze married Kathy Barber and had a son, Freddie Prinze, Jr., in 1976. == References == == Other websites == Category:1954 births Category:1977 deaths Category:Actors from New York City Category:Comedians from New York City Category:American Roman Catholics Category:American stand-up comedians Category:American television actors Category:Suicides by firearm in the United States
